Class MoxyJsonContextResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.gsfc.spdf.ssc.MoxyJsonContextResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    jakarta.ws.rs.ext.ContextResolver<org.glassfish.jersey.moxy.json.MoxyJsonConfig>
    public class MoxyJsonContextResolver
extends java.lang.Object
implements jakarta.ws.rs.ext.ContextResolver<org.glassfish.jersey.moxy.json.MoxyJsonConfig>
    This class implements a ContextResolver for the EclipseLink MOXy JSON provider. It exists in order to customize MOXy for the SSC web services. To date, no helpful configuration has been found. You would only need this class or JacksonJsonContextResolver -- not both.
    Author:
    B. Harris
